---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer id="contact" class="footer">
  <div class="footer-wave">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 120" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,60 C240,120 480,0 720,60 C960,120 1200,0 1440,60 L1440,120 L0,120 Z" fill="var(--color-dark)"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <!-- Brand -->
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <div class="footer-logo">
            <img src="/images/nvb-logo-only.png" alt="NARAHA VERO BASE" class="footer-logo-img" />
          </div>
          <p class="footer-tagline">自転車とキャンプで、地域に新しい<br>「人の流れ」と「物語」をつくる</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Event Info -->
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3 class="footer-heading">開催情報</h3>
          <ul class="footer-list">
            <li>📅 2026年6月13日(土)・14日(日)</li>
            <li>📍 天神岬スポーツ公園キャンプ場（福島県楢葉町）</li>
            <li>🎟️ 入場無料（宿泊キャンプは要チケット）</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="footer-org-details">
            <p>主催：楢葉町</p>
            <p>共催：福島民報社</p>
            <p>運営：一般社団法人自転車キャンプツーリズム協会</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Links -->
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3 class="footer-heading">リンク</h3>
          <ul class="footer-list">
            <li><a href="#introduction" class="footer-link">ABOUT</a></li>
            <li><a href="#overview" class="footer-link">概要</a></li>
            <li><a href="#experience" class="footer-link">CONTENTS</a></li>
            <li><a href="#venue" class="footer-link">会場</a></li>
            <li><a href="#news" class="footer-link">NEWS</a></li>
            <li><a href="#faq" class="footer-link">FAQ</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact" class="footer-link">CONTACT</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Buttons -->
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3 class="footer-heading">チケット・出展</h3>
          <div class="footer-buttons">
            <a href="https://select-type.com/ev/?ev=WMSza2cQpKQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="footer-btn-primary">⛺ 宿泊予約はこちらから</a>
            <a href="https://select-type.com/ev/?ev=nyKigfrgODM" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="footer-btn-secondary">
              🏢 ご出展希望の方はこちらから
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Organizer -->
      <div class="footer-organizer">
        <p>主催: 楢葉町 ／ 共催: 福島民報社 ／ 運営: 一般社団法人自転車キャンプツーリズム協会</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; {currentYear} NARAHA VERO BASE. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    position: relative;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .footer-wave {
    position: relative;
    height: 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .footer-wave svg {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .footer-content {
    background: var(--color-dark);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .footer-content {
      padding: 4rem 3rem 2rem;
    }
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .footer-logo {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-logo-img {
    height: 80px;
    width: auto;
  }

  .footer-tagline {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }

  .footer-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--color-sunset-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .footer-org-details {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }

  .footer-link {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .footer-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-ocean-light);
  }

  .footer-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .footer-btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-sunset), var(--color-coral));
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .footer-btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .footer-btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .footer-organizer {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }
</style>
